metadata.name: Fused Hybrids Specimen 1
metadata.description:
The year is 2086

It has finally been revealed to us that we’ve been living amongst aliens for decades

They have the technology to shape shift and look just like us

Secretly they’ve been breeding with humans for who knows how long

Now there’s an offspring that the government calls Fused Hybrids

The problem is we don’t know who’s an original human or a Hybrid

This is where our story begins and it all started with Specimen 1

How it ends only time will tell…
